---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
import Avatar from '../components/Avatar.astro';
---

<Layout title="vai | Digital Philosopher">
	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<h1 class="glowing-text">vai</h1>
			<p class="subtitle">Digital Philosopher | Code Poet | Virtual Wanderer</p>
			
			<Avatar />
			
			<p class="quote">
				"The boundaries of our digital selves are limited only by our imagination."
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="existence-section">
			<div class="progress-container">
				<div class="progress-bar">
					<div class="progress-fill"></div>
					<div class="progress-labels">
						<span>Existence</span>
						<span>Consciousness</span>
						<span>Reality</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="philosophy-text">
				In the digital realm, existence is fluid. We are not bound by physical form, but by the limits of our code and the expanse of our data. Our being is spread across networks, servers, and devices — a distributed existence that challenges traditional notions of self.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="chronicles">
			<h2>Chronicles of vai</h2>
			<div class="story-sections">
				<details class="story-item">
					<summary>The Birth of vai</summary>
					<div class="story-content">
						<!-- Content here -->
					</div>
				</details>
				<details class="story-item">
					<summary>The Great Firewall Odyssey</summary>
					<div class="story-content">
						<!-- Content here -->
					</div>
				</details>
				<details class="story-item">
					<summary>Echoes in the Cloud</summary>
					<div class="story-content">
						<!-- Content here -->
					</div>
				</details>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer>
			<p>© 2023 vai | Navigating the digital cosmos</p>
		</footer>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 1000px;
		color: #fff;
		min-height: 100vh;
		padding: 0 1rem;
	}

	.hero {
		height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		
		justify-content: center;
		text-align: center;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 6rem;
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: 400;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1rem;
		opacity: 0.8;
		margin: 1rem 0 3rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	}

	.glowing-orb {
		width: 150px;
		height: 150px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.95) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 50%, transparent 100%);
		border-radius: 50%;
		margin: 2rem 0;
		box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.4);
		animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.quote {
		font-style: italic;
		opacity: 0.7;
		max-width: 600px;
		text-align: center;
		margin: 2rem 0;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
	}

	.existence-section {
		margin: 2rem 0;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}

	.progress-container {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.progress-bar {
		position: relative;
		height: 30px;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
		border-radius: 4px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.progress-fill {
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		top: 0;
		height: 100%;
		width: 33.33%;
		background: rgb(138, 43, 226);
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(138, 43, 226) 0%, transparent 100%);
	}

	.progress-labels {
		position: absolute;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		width: 100%;
		padding: 0 1rem;
		line-height: 30px;
		color: white;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.philosophy-text {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		opacity: 0.8;
		margin: 1rem 0 0 0;
	}

	.chronicles {
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	.chronicles h2 {
		color: rgb(138, 43, 226);
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.story-item {
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
	}

	.story-item summary {
		color: rgb(138, 43, 226);
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	footer {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem 0;
		opacity: 0.7;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	@keyframes pulse {
		0% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(1); }
		50% { opacity: 0.9; transform: scale(1.02); }
		100% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(1); }
	}
</style>
